File contents: Records of contact between several Legionnaires, and members of the Syndicate. Looks like they've been in cahoots after all… There's not a lot here, but it could go a long way in convincing the other syndicate families that the Shaw's are up to no good.
Virus is copying all the data in the network to a private Syndicate server off-site. Looks like Darrius wanted some assurance that the Legion weren't going to stab him in the back.
